U+03c4~}{~GREEK SMALL LETTER ETA WITH PERISPOMENI U+1fc6~}{~GREEK SMALL
LETTER MU U+03bc~}{~GREEK SMALL LETTER ALPHA U+03b1~}, {~GREEK SMALL
